{{{html}}}
<div class='upgrade-cta' lang='en'>
    {{#has visibility='paid'}}
        <h2>
            This post is for premium members only
        </h2>
        <p>
            Join the 100+ developers and entrepreneur, premium members of our
            community and get full access to our library of private posts.
        </p>
    {{else}}
        <h2>
            This post is for members only
        </h2>
