            Join the 100+ developers and entrepreneur, members of our community
            and get access to our library of member-only posts.
        </p>
    {{/has}}
    <a href='/membership/' class='button'>Subscribe!</a>
    <p class='switch'>
        Already a member?
        <a href='/login/'>Log in</a>
    </p>
